A SMILE - a Self-Motivated Impact Learning Environment.
In this method, students go through a 5-step process to encourage themselves, ignite their own curiosity, find inner passions, collaborate with like-minded individuals who share similar goals and who are discovering the same subjects, and finally to engage in 
community development to share wisdom back with those who need it most.
